race.comment: Very even. DREAMSTONE (6) is a free-running type in good form. Gave a sight but run down last time and drawn to give a sight again. AZEOLA (5) continued the recent good form with a determined win over a similar distance last time. Aided by the claim again and with just a little more weight will be tough to stop again. BELLMAN (1) is another racing in great form. Has won his last two and has run well here. Stretches out further this time but on recent figures right in this. OVERLOADED (7) was narrowly beaten two back then found the grade a bit rich last time. This easier and will be tough to hold out. GREAT PROSPERITY (2) had placed three on end before a deserved win last time. Has a bit more weight bit hard to fault consistent recent form.
race.rail_position: +4m from the 400m to the winning post, True Remainder. (Pent: 5.60)
